data.description: Step into the warmth of a timeless 1975 rambler, situated on an expansive almost 2-acre lot. This generous abode boasts 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and 4,448 sqft of versatile living space, offering the canvas for new chapters and lasting memories.  The journey begins with a welcoming foyer, adorned with stunning laminate flooring that sets the stage for a grand entrance. To the right, a sizable living room beckons, promising moments of togetherness and relaxation. Straight ahead, an expansive eat-in kitchen awaits, with abundant storage and seamless access to the inviting back deck, the perfect stage for your next barbecue.  The primary bedroom is generously sized, providing room for a cozy sitting area and showcasing a well-appointed ensuite. Completing the upper level are three additional spacious bedrooms and a guest bath, making this space ideal for family and guests alike.  Venturing downstairs, you'll discover a basement brimming with potential, ready for your creative touch and personal staging. An additional large room with an adjacent bathroom can serve as a 5th bedroom or a home office, providing flexibility to suit your needs. The laundry room on this level offers ample space to cater to all your washing needs.  Storage is abundant throughout this home, not just in terms of size but also through the inclusion of a dedicated storage room and a capacious garage.  Outside, picturesque views and an expansive yard await, providing the ideal setting for new pets and children to frolic and play. This home is more than a structure; it's a haven for cherished moments, a vessel for new memories waiting to be created. Embrace the opportunity to make this space your own and craft a lifetime of unforgettable experiences
